page.title: 08Farnham Town Boys F.C.
page.content: Farnham Town is the really big team in this area. There are lots of different leagues in this area and the under 13's belong to the{West Surrey } league. The youngest age group are the under 9's,and from that age group it goes up to the under 16's. There is a {youth team}and a men's team as well. I belong to the under13's. I joined about three months ago from another team. Last season the under 13's came third in the league,out of about 15 other teams. The colour of the kit is {charet, blue and white.}The teams are managed by mainly Dads of boys at Farnham Town. The managers do not get paid at all.
